<h1>Report for meter <%= @meter.school.name %> <small class="text-muted"><%= @meter.display_name %></small></h1>
<p><%= link_to 'School group meter report', admin_school_group_meter_report_path(@meter.school.school_group), class: 'btn btn-success' %></p>

<h2>Validated meter readings</h2>
<p>Dates start at date of first recorded reading, <%= @first_reading %>, up until the present day.</p><p>There is usually a delay of a few days before receiving meter readings, hence the last few days will usually have no readings.</p>

<div id="calendar" class="calendar"></div>

<div class='calendar-legend row'>
  <div class='legend-scale vertical'>
    <ul class='legend-labels'>
      <% @colour_hash.each do |type, colour| %>
        <li><span style='background:<%= colour %>;'></span><%= "#{@amr_types[type][:name]} (#{type})" %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
